h1_title: The Beguiling Chant of the Pagoda Realm
content: Just past the duo, you'll find an open gate leading back to the outer ring, while the interior passageway also continues. If you dip out for a moment, you can look right back the way you came to find two enemies guarding a green Wisp by a pile of rubble with another Yaksha Archer at the top.
promot:
This is an excerpt from the file 'Pagoda_Realm_Walkthrough.md', within the main section titled 'The Beguiling Chant of the Pagoda Realm', specifically from the subsection 'Lower Pagoda (Level 1)'.
The content is as follows:
Just past the duo, you'll find an open gate leading back to the outer ring, while the interior passageway also continues. If you dip out for a moment, you can look right back the way you came to find two enemies guarding a green Wisp by a pile of rubble with another Yaksha Archer at the top.
